Newly-opened station serving the southern portion of Tanjong Katong

To reach the northern portion of Tanjong Katong, its easier to take bus 30 from Dakota MRT station, rather than walking the entire way down the road.
Beautiful station. Modern and clean. Location is questionable since its mostly surrounded by condos and landed properties.
